Description: wiki-ingest — align deletion safety check with OBSIDIAN_RAW_DIR
 Audit B2 (docs/260418-dual-sensitivity-analysis.md §5.2) flags
 `.skills/wiki-ingest/SKILL.md` line 64 as requiring the resolved path
 to be inside `$OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH/_raw/`. In dual-zone deployments the
 raw staging directory is outside the vault (configured via
 `OBSIDIAN_RAW_DIR`), so this literal check would refuse to delete any
 promoted file — blocking the `wiki-ingest` raw-mode workflow.
 .
 This patch replaces the hard-coded `$OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH/_raw/` guard
 with `$OBSIDIAN_RAW_DIR`, so the safety check follows the configured
 staging directory.
 .
 Composition with B1 : this patch's baseline is the post-B1 state of
 `.skills/wiki-ingest/SKILL.md` (line 62 already rewritten). Apply
 order : B1 → B2. Running B2 alone against the pristine vendor tree
 will fail the `git apply --check`.
